author: Red Means Recording
description:
Get COLORCOMA here: https://redmeansrecording.gumroad.com/l/colorcoma

COLORCOMA is a preset pack for the Elektron Syntakt featuring presets made for my videos, live shows, jams, and all other Syntakt-related stuff since I got it. It's appropriate for pretty much any genre of electronic music except happy hardcore. Sorry.

You get 204 presets
12 Demo Patterns
11 Song mini-EP

Preset breakdown: 
29 BASSES
10 BASS DRUMS
17 CHORDS
07 CLAPS
13 EFFECTS
12 HIHATS
41 LEADS
08 PERCS
02 RIDES
12 SNARES
53 SYNTHS
